158
00:11:54,506 --> 00:11:58,010
Pascal Sauvage,
jumped-up Frenchman.

159
00:11:58,093 --> 00:12:01,096
Lorna Campbell. I've been so looking
forward to meeting you.

160
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,724
- Enchanté.

161
00:12:03,807 --> 00:12:06,894
But of course! You're Johnny English.
I've heard all about you.

162
00:12:06,977 --> 00:12:10,480
