173
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:05,202
As we stand here
in the Tower of London,

174
00:13:05,285 --> 00:13:07,371
the most famous prison
in the world,

175
00:13:07,454 --> 00:13:10,916
where these wonderful
jewels will rest safely...

176
