178
00:13:15,963 --> 00:13:19,132
for giving me
this wonderful experience...

179
00:13:19,216 --> 00:13:23,637
to contribute to the restoration
of these jewels.

180
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:28,058
It was, as we say in France,
le top, le best of.

181
00:13:28,141 --> 00:13:30,561
- And what a beautiful...

