213
00:16:12,639 --> 00:16:18,437
- Hair colour?
- Um... orange.

214
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:21,565
- Orange?
- Mmm. And curly.

215
00:16:21,648 --> 00:16:25,277
Well, frizzy, actually.
Frizzy sort of thing.

216
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:27,821
- Frizzy.
- An eyepatch.

217
00:16:27,905 --> 00:16:31,366
Broken nose.
Very few teeth.

218
00:16:31,450 --> 00:16:33,702
Two, I would say,
at the most.

219
00:16:33,785 --> 00:16:37,039
And a scar on his cheek...

220
00:16:37,122 --> 00:16:41,376
